title: Microsoft Windows XP Professional SP3 Integrated November 2010
description:
Microsoft Windows XP Professional SP3 Integrated November 2010 + SATA Drivers By Maher


This is the original Microsoft Windows XP Professional SP3 ISO (Volume License) including Microsoft updates til November 2010 and SATA drivers.

There's no serial needed during installation, the key is already inserted.

Notice: Windows Messenger and MSN Explorer were removed.
